&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A day in the life&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate delivery across multiple client accounts, driving the best strategy and/or execution to meet clients’ needs in an agile and responsive way&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage multiple projects simultaneously and understand project priorities in the context of agency and client expectations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate and monitor the work of internal delivery teams to complete tasks on time and within budget&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to the production, delivery, and QA of emails, social media content, and web pages&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Plan, schedule, and estimate costs of new and existing business&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Draft client-facing proposals and memoranda, presentations, strategic plans, and other internal or client-facing materials&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Have a clear view of Blue State’s various offerings and identify opportunities to add value and support clients’ needs as they expand or change&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Have a finger on the pulse of cutting-edge developments taking place in tech and digital organizing - inviting opinions from peers and sharing our point of view with clients&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
