&lt;li&gt;$1,000 annually in professional development funds&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Competitive health, dental, and vision insurance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Flexible and health savings accounts&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;401K &amp;amp; employer match&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Generous paid holiday schedule&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;12-week fully-paid parental leave for all parents-to-be&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Short-term and long-term disability insurance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Pre-tax commuter benefits&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Remote work flexibility&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
