&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What to know&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Help us land our dream clients — and yours. &lt;/strong&gt;We are seeking a Business Development Manager to join our Partnerships team to provide support to our business development team and help us grow our business. The ideal candidate is an excellent project manager and writer and has demonstrated success supporting sales or account management at an agency, consulting, or communications firm.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will support the Partnerships team in the pursuit of new business opportunities and help develop and manage a sales pipeline. You will work across the agency and with cross-discipline teams to develop proposals, pitches, presentations, and new scopes of work. You will help draft and project manage these deliverables and support agency thought leadership internally and externally.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a rare opportunity to work with a client base that spans nonprofit, advocacy, corporate, and political campaign sectors. If you want to be a part of driving real change in the progressive space, then this might be the position for you.&lt;/p&gt;
