&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;A day in the life&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Manage the sales process for proposal development, pitches, and outbound efforts:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Help the Partnerships team sell Blue State’s offerings and services to brands, nonprofits, advocacy organizations, and progressive political candidates and organizations&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Project manage and help draft memos, proposals, pitch decks, and related collateral in collaboration with creative, strategy, and technical teams, delivering first-rate materials that target an audience of industry leaders and C-Suite executives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide logistical support and process management throughout the sales lifecycle — from the proposal and pitch process through contracting&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead qualifying calls and discussions with prospective clients in partnership with VPs and SVPs on the Partnerships team&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Effectively communicate and strategize with internal teams to help meet prospective clients’ goals and their organizational objectives throughout the sales process&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Help build, manage, and continually develop a sales pipeline to achieve new business targets:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with senior Partnerships leaders to bring in new leads across targeted verticals through traditional and creative approaches to outbound sales&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct research on Blue State leads, prospects, and clients, and clearly communicate findings to senior leadership&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leverage SalesForce to help manage, track and operationalize the sales pipeline; pull reports and contribute to ongoing business analysis as needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
